General.Name: Besqab publ AB
General.Description: Besqab AB (publ) operates as a housing developer in Sweden. It offers property development and management; and real estate development, including development of rental housing, care properties, and other community services. The company was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Danderyd, Sweden.
